{
  "script_id": "stern-brocot",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "所有的正分数，能不能一个不漏地排成一棵树？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "答案是可以，这棵树叫做 Stern-Brocot 树。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "它从两个最简单的边界出发：零分之一，和一分之零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "在它们之间，一条规则就长出了全部分数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "mediant",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "mediant-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/mediant-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "两个分数的中位数，就是把分子相加、分母相加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "mediant",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "mediant-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/mediant-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "零一和一零的中位数，是一分之一，正好落在它们中间，成为树根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "mediant",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "mediant-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/mediant-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "再对左右两段各取中位数，就分出下一层，如此递归生长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "reduced",
      "line_id": "red-1",
      "filename": "reduced-red-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/reduced-red-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "神奇的是，这样生成的每个分数，天生就是既约的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "reduced",
      "line_id": "red-2",
      "filename": "reduced-red-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/reduced-red-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.39,
      "size": 22176,
      "text": "分子分母永远互质，用不着再约分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "reduced",
      "line_id": "red-3",
      "filename": "reduced-red-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/reduced-red-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "而且每个正既约分数都恰好出现一次，不重复也不遗漏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "cf",
      "line_id": "cf-1",
      "filename": "cf-cf-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/cf-cf-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "从树根往下走，每一步只有向左或向右两种选择。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "cf",
      "line_id": "cf-2",
      "filename": "cf-cf-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/cf-cf-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "这串左右指令，恰好就是这个分数的连分数展开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "展开更多层，看分数如何一层层细密地铺满数轴。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "注意每一层的分数，都被上一层的中位数整齐地隔开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "中位数规则，把全部既约分数排成一棵有序的树。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "每个分数唯一现身，路径又暗合连分数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stern-brocot",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stern-brocot/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "简单的相加，装下了无穷的分数世界，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 31.81,
